10633 #define TRANSCODE_TABLE_INFO utf8_mac_byte_array, 9970, utf8_mac_word_array, 5805, ((int)sizeof(unsigned int))
10634 static const rb_transcoder
10635 rb_to_UTF8_MAC = {
10636     "UTF-8", "UTF8-MAC", to_UTF8_MAC,
10637     TRANSCODE_TABLE_INFO,
10638     1, /* input_unit_length */
10639     4, /* max_input */
10640     9, /* max_output */
10641     asciicompat_converter, /* asciicompat_type */
10642     0, NULL, NULL, /* state_size, state_init, state_fini */
10643     NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL,
10644     NULL, NULL, NULL

10647 
10648 #define BYTE_ADDR(index) (utf8_mac_byte_array + (index))
10649 #define WORD_ADDR(index) (utf8_mac_word_array + INFO2WORDINDEX(index))
10650 #define BL_BASE BYTE_ADDR(BYTE_LOOKUP_BASE(WORD_ADDR(next_info)))
10651 #define BL_INFO WORD_ADDR(BYTE_LOOKUP_INFO(WORD_ADDR(next_info)))
10652 #define BL_MIN_BYTE     (BL_BASE[0])
10653 #define BL_MAX_BYTE     (BL_BASE[1])
10654 #define BL_OFFSET(byte) (BL_BASE[2+(byte)-BL_MIN_BYTE])
10655 #define BL_ACTION(byte) (BL_INFO[BL_OFFSET((byte))])
10656 
10657 #define STATUS_BUF_SIZE 16
10658 struct from_utf8_mac_status {
10659     unsigned char buf[STATUS_BUF_SIZE];
10660     int beg;
10661     int end;
10662     int len;
10663 };
10664 #define buf_length(sp) ((sp)->len)
10665 
10666 int
10667 buf_bytesize(struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp)
10668 {
10669     int size = sp->end - sp->beg + STATUS_BUF_SIZE;
10670     size %= STATUS_BUF_SIZE;
10671     return size;
10672 }
10673 
10674 void
10675 buf_push(struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp, const unsigned char *p, ssize_t l)
10676 {
10677     const unsigned char *pend = p + l;
10678     while (p < pend) {
10679         sp->buf[sp->end++] = *p++;
10680         sp->end %= STATUS_BUF_SIZE;
10681     }
10682     sp->len++;
10683 }
10684 
10685 unsigned char
10686 buf_shift(struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp)
10687 {
10688     unsigned char c = sp->buf[sp->beg++];
10689     sp->beg %= STATUS_BUF_SIZE;
10690     if ((c & 0xC0) != 0x80) sp->len--;
10691     return c;
10692 }
10693 
10694 void
10695 buf_shift_char(struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp)
10696 {
10697     if (sp->beg == sp->end) return;
10698     do {
10699         buf_shift(sp);
10700     } while (sp->beg != sp->end && (sp->buf[sp->beg] & 0xC0) == 0x80);
10701 }
10702 
10703 void
10704 buf_clear(struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp)
10705 {
10706     sp->beg = sp->end = sp->len = 0;
10707 }
10708 
10709 unsigned char
10710 buf_at(struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp, int pos)
10711 {
10712     pos += sp->beg;
10713     pos %= STATUS_BUF_SIZE;
10714     return sp->buf[pos];
10715 }
10716 
10717 int
10718 buf_output_char(struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp, unsigned char *o)
10719 {
10720     int n = 0;
10721     while (sp->beg != sp->end) {
10722         o[n++] = buf_shift(sp);
10723         if ((sp->buf[sp->beg] & 0xC0) != 0x80) break;
10724     }
10725     return n;
10726 }
10727 
10728 int
10729 buf_output_all(struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp, unsigned char *o)
10730 {
10731     int n = 0;
10732     while (sp->beg != sp->end) {
10733         o[n++] = buf_shift(sp);
10734     }
10735     return n;
10736 }
10737 
10738 VALUE
10739 get_info(VALUE next_info, struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp) {
10740     int pos = 0;
10741     while (pos < buf_bytesize(sp)) {
10742         unsigned char next_byte = buf_at(sp, pos++);
10743         if (next_byte < BL_MIN_BYTE || BL_MAX_BYTE < next_byte)
10744             next_info = INVALID;
10745         else {
10746             next_info = (VALUE)BL_ACTION(next_byte);
10747         }
10748         if ((next_info & 3) == 0) continue;
10749         break;
10750     }
10751     return next_info;
10752 }
10753 
10754 int
10755 buf_apply(int mode, struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp, unsigned char *o)
10756 {
10757     int n = 0;
10758     VALUE next_info = mode == 3 ? from_utf8_mac_nfc3 : from_utf8_mac_nfc2;
10759     next_info = get_info(next_info, sp);
10760     switch (next_info & 0x1F) {
10761       case THREEbt:
10762       case TWObt:
10763         o[n++] = getBT1(next_info);
10764         o[n++] = getBT2(next_info);
10765         if (THREEbt == (next_info & 0x1F)) o[n++] = getBT3(next_info);
10766         if (mode == 3) {
10767             buf_clear(sp);
10768         }
10769         else {
10770             buf_shift_char(sp);
10771             buf_shift_char(sp);
10772         }
10773         break;
10774       default:
10775         return 0;
10776     }
10777     return n;
10778 }
10779 
10780 static int
10781 from_utf8_mac_init(void *statep)
10782 {
10783     struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp = statep;
10784     buf_clear(sp);
10785     return 0;
10786 }
10787 
10788 static ssize_t
10789 from_utf8_mac_finish(void *statep,
10790         unsigned char *o, size_t osize)
10791 {
10792     struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp = statep;
10793     int n;
10794     if (buf_length(sp) == 0) return 0;
10795     n = buf_apply(2, sp, o) + buf_output_all(sp, o);
10796     return n;
10797 }
10798 
10799 static ssize_t
10800 fun_so_from_utf8_mac(void *statep,
10801         const unsigned char *s, size_t l,
10802         unsigned char *o, size_t osize)
10803 {
10804     struct from_utf8_mac_status *sp = statep;
10805     ssize_t n = 0;
10806 
10807     switch (l) {
10808       case 1:
10809         n = from_utf8_mac_finish(sp, o, osize);
10810         break;
10811       case 4:
10812         n = from_utf8_mac_finish(sp, o, osize);
10813         o[n++] = *s++;
10814         o[n++] = *s++;
10815         o[n++] = *s++;
10816         o[n++] = *s++;
10817         return n;
10818     }
10819 
10820     buf_push(sp, s, l);
10821     if (buf_length(sp) < 3) return n;
10822 
10823     n = buf_apply(3, sp, o);
10824     if (n > 0) return n;
10825 
10826     n = buf_apply(2, sp, o);
10827     if (n > 0) return n;
10828 
10829     return buf_output_char(sp, o);
10830 }

10833 rb_from_UTF8_MAC = {
10834     "UTF8-MAC", "UTF-8", from_UTF8_MAC,
10835     TRANSCODE_TABLE_INFO,
10836     1, /* input_unit_length */
10837     4, /* max_input */
10838     10, /* max_output */
10839     asciicompat_encoder, /* asciicompat_type */
10840     sizeof(struct from_utf8_mac_status), from_utf8_mac_init, from_utf8_mac_init,
10841     NULL, NULL, NULL, fun_so_from_utf8_mac,
10842     from_utf8_mac_finish
10843 };
